title: BUBBLE WOODS
description: Enter the magical forest and earn as many points as you can in 60 seconds! Your goal in this fast-paced bubble shooter is to match 3 or more bubbles of the same color to pop them. Play smart and bounce balls off the walls to reach strategically important bubbles - dropping big clusters can give you a huge bonus! Use powerful boosters to score even more points and try to reach the highest score!
